### Hadith 1:727

*Narrated Abu Ma'mar:*

I asked Khabbab whether the Prophet used to recite the Qur'an in the
Zuhr and the 'Asr prayers. He replied in the affirmative. We said, "How
did you come to know that?" He said, "From the movement of his beard."

